OL,3,CWhy Wes Streeting is abolishing NHS
OL,4,CEngland
OL,6,FThe mystery about the abolition by
OL,7,FStreeting and Starmer of NHS England
OL,8,Fis not why they are doing it, but that
OL,9,Fthe previous Tory government chose not
OL,10,Fto.
OL,12,FBecause the health secretary's
OL,13,Frationale is that so much of what NHS
OL,14,FEngland does is expensively duplicated
OL,15,Fin his Department for Health and
OL,16,FSocial Care. To put it in the simplest
OL,17,Fterms, when he wants official advice
OL,18,Fon some element of NHS management or
OL,19,Fpolicy, he'd rather hear one coherent
OL,20,Fvoice rather than two competing ones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
