OL,3,CWhy Wes Streeting is abolishing NHS
OL,4,CEngland
OL,6,FThat said, Streeting is taking a big
OL,7,Frisk.
OL,9,FIn order to save more than #500m in
OL,10,Fwages and related costs, he has
OL,11,Fordered a 50% reduction in NHS
OL,12,FEngland's 15,300 headcount straight
OL,13,Faway. These are the jobs that
OL,14,Freplicate functions at the Department
OL,15,Fof Health and Social Care.
OL,17,FBut he is asking the remaining 7,650
OL,18,Fto take on an important new set of
OL,19,Fresponsibilities in NHS England's
OL,20,Fremaining two years of existence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
