OL,4,CEngland
OL,6,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,7,Four political experts are across all
OL,8,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,9,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,11,FFirst they will need to better monitor
OL,12,Flocal health providers, intervene when
OL,13,Fthings are going badly, and reward
OL,14,Fthose performing well with more
OL,15,Fcapital for investment.
OL,17,FSecond, they will initiate central
OL,18,Fprocurement of expensive medical kit,
OL,19,Fto get better deals than decentralised
OL,20,Fpurchasers and faster deals for
OL,21,Fexciting new tech.
