OL,3,CWhy Wes Streeting is abolishing NHS
OL,4,CEngland
OL,6,FThird, they will be asked to replicate
OL,7,Fthe success of vaccine development
OL,8,Fduring the COVID crisis by
OL,9,Fcentralising cutting edge research,
OL,10,Ftrials and testing in partnership with
OL,11,Flife sciences and pharmaceuticals
OL,12,Ffirms.
OL,14,FThis is big stuff. And Streeting will
OL,15,Fbe asking a workforce likely to be
OL,16,Fchronically unsettled and demoralised
OL,17,Fby not knowing whether they'll have a
OL,18,Fjob in two years.
