OL,3,CWhy Wes Streeting is abolishing NHS
OL,4,CEngland
OL,6,FManaging job cuts while trying to
OL,7,Fimprove NHS performance will be tricky
OL,8,Ffor Streeting. And with the abolition
OL,9,Fof NHS England he has no one else to
OL,10,Fblame if all or any of it goes pear
OL,11,Fshaped.
